OL,3,GUK long range forecast
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Tue 26 May to Thu 4 Jun
OL,6,FTemperatures will fall through this
OL,7,Fperiod to be above normal but not as
OL,8,Fhot as through the preceding Bank
OL,9,FHoliday weekend. With high pressure
OL,10,Fexpected to remain in place for much
OL,11,Fof the UK, fine weather is likely to
OL,12,Fcontinue for most places. Some patchy
OL,13,Frain may affect the far north at times
OL,14,Fand perhaps a few showers in the far
OL,15,Fsouth. Temperatures are expected to be
OL,16,Fabove normal overall, feeling very
OL,17,Fwarm at times with light winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
